// Database Design Standards (MUST follow):
//  ✅ UUID primary keys — use @id @default(uuid())
//  ✅ snake_case field names — e.g., created_at, user_id
//  ✅ created_at and updated_at timestamps on every model
//  ✅ Explicit @map() for table names if needed
//  ❌ NEVER use auto-increment integer IDs (@default(autoincrement()))
